headline: BLK & Jio Financial's JV Gets Approval to Act as Investment Adviser
summary: BlackRock & Jio Financial JV, Jio BlackRock, secures SEBI approval to act as an investment adviser, deepening its push into India's asset management market.

headline: Retail Investors Risk Ominous Opportunity Cost With Private Investments, Moody’s Warns
summary: The private sector took off after traditional banks pulled back from some risky lending following the 2008 financial crisis.
